            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows mild leukopenia, which may indicate a transient or chronic reduction in white blood cells. All red blood cell parameters and platelets are within normal limits, except for a markedly elevated platelet distribution width, which may suggest increased platelet size variability, possibly due to platelet activation or turnover. Clinical correlation and follow-up are recommended.</td></tr></table></div>"
